parameters:
\n<Yuuki>It's been a while since I wore this, but I think I
can still pull it off, right~?

\n<Yuuki>Maybe next time I'll invite Rui-chan to do a high
school uniform matching thing-?

\n<Yuuki>I've seen videos of people renting out school
buildings, but I wonder how much that costs...

\n<Yuuki>But just a school building and uniforms might lack
a twist, right? If we're going to rent a place,
maybe inviting a bunch of people and doing a
Japanese-style clothing match would be cool!

\n<Yuuki>Speaking of which, she's slow to reply... Maybe
Rui-chan went on a trip by herself again?

\n<Tv Audio>This is the recent mass abduction case targeting
young women, and here are the names of those who
are believed to be victims.

\n<Yuuki>Ugh... Haven't dozens of people gone missing
already?

\n<Tv Audio>If you are not involved in the incident and your
name appears here, or if you are with someone
whose name is listed, please contact the police
for case organization

\n<Yuuki>Wow, that's crazy... The number has increased
again.
